preference.preference_description:
This preference is used to configure TcRA Report display for application locations.TcRA Report will be displayed in TcRA Viewer. This Viewer will be inserted as a 'Dashboard' Sub-location. Pre-defined application location will only have this sub-location inserted.Values should follow below pattern:
LocationName:{Report1Information}
e.g.
Home:{"name":"Home Summary Overview", "type":"Report"}
